WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.200
Welcome to AiFetchly Market Insight Explorer. This walkthrough shows how to turn public search results into qualified leads.

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:11.000
Start in the left navigation. Open Market Insight, then choose Market Insight Explorer.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:17.300
Add one keyword per line, then choose Google, Bing, or Yandex. Ignore other engines for this workflow.

00:00:17.300 --> 00:00:23.500
For Yandex, set Use local browser to Yes. For large Google or Bing runs, proxies and accounts improve reliability.

00:00:23.500 --> 00:00:29.300
Use Search Task List to monitor status, retry failures, edit settings, stop running jobs, and open results.

00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:35.500
Select result rows, run AI analysis, open profile insights, build contact profiles, and export the best leads.

00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:42.000
Small batches, good proxies, local browser, and AI scoring make Market Insight Explorer more reliable and more useful.
